<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ gào sù wǒ rú hé xiàn shàng wǒ de shēng mìng, dài xī wàng rù rén qún zhōng;
 zhǔ gào sù wǒ rú hé fù shàng wǒ de guān huái, jiāng wēn nuǎn dài rù shì jiè.
 wǒ kàn dào líng hún zhōng de yōu shāng, gū dú zhōng rén de xīn zài jiǎo luò chàn dǒu.
 chà qiǎn wǒ, chà qiǎn wǒ, wǒ yuàn fù chū wǒ suǒ yǒu,
 chà qiǎn wǒ dào xū yào nǐ de rén qún zhōng;
 chōng mǎn wǒ, chōng mǎn wǒ, yòng nǐ ài lái chōng mǎn wǒ,
 zài yī cì jǐn wò tā men de shǒu</lyrics>
<title>chà qiǎn wǒ</title>
</song>